comment:
This is all speculation, but to armchair the situation, I would say that it is highly likely that heard abused Elon Musk as well based on her past history of domestic abuse as well as the obvious injuries to Elon's face. Now, it is possible that he got those injuries in any number of ways, so I won't ever say without evidence that it was amber's doing, but from the pictures, the wounds do look like they come from being struck in the face. Additionally, if Elon and heard decided to stay together after breaking up to maintain appearances, it could have been to dissuade the public from speculation of domestic abuse and, given heard's obsession with her image and Musk's nonconfrontational and reserved nature, he might have gone along with it to avoid tabloids and drama. 

One thing that I believe is evident from the pictures of them together is that Musk was not happy being with her. The look on his face in all those pictures is not that of a happy man. Also, the way he is holding her hand looks very firm and begrudging, not relaxed as it would be if he actually wanted to hold her hand. He looks like he would rather be anywhere else with anyone else in all those pictures. None of that is definitively indicative of domestic abuse and it could have just been an unhappy relationship, but I don't believe it can be ruled out.

Unfortunately, there is no actual evidence in these pictures and articles that would be admissible in court, but it is possible that evidence exists with Elon Musk that would help Johnny's case. I believe that it is ultimately up to Elon himself to insert himself in any of the ongoing legal cases, but that if he does have any sort of evidence, he should provide it in the interest of justice for himself as well as Johnny and all abused men
